B.G1=new A.o("Injury to which structure in DAI results in severe memory impairment?","Fornix.")
B.F6=new A.o("Which MRI sequence is 3-6 times more sensitive than conventional GRE for detecting hemorrhagic DAI?","Susceptibility Weighted Imaging (SWI).")
B.GD=new A.o("What is the imaging biomarker of choice for identifying subtle DAI when conventional MRI is normal?","Diffusion Tensor Imaging (DTI) showing decreased fractional anisotropy.")
B.Fr=new A.o("What is the primary difference between primary and secondary brain injury in terms of clinical management?","Secondary injury is potentially preventable and treatable.")
B.GJ=new A.o("In the excitotoxicity cascade, massive calcium influx activates which enzymes that lead to cellular destruction?","Calpains, lipases, and endonucleases.")
B.GQ=new A.o("According to the Giza & Hovda model, what causes the 'hyperglycolysis' phase after concussion?","Na+/K+ ATPase pumps working overtime to restore ionic balance.")
