B.FA=new A.o("How much does glymphatic clearance increase during sleep compared to wakefulness?","60%.")
B.H5=new A.o("Where does tau protein typically deposit in Chronic Traumatic Encephalopathy (CTE)?","Sulcal depths in a perivascular distribution.")
B.EY=new A.o("Term: Cortical spreading depolarization (CSD)","Definition: Waves of near-complete neuronal depolarization propagating across the cortex at 2-5 mm/min.")
B.Ed=new A.o("How does TBI affect the gut-brain axis within hours of injury?","It increases intestinal permeability ('leaky gut') and causes gut dysbiosis.")
B.FY=new A.o("What were the results of Phase III clinical trials (ProTECT III/SyNAPSe) regarding progesterone in TBI?","They showed no benefit over placebo.")
