B.FC=new A.o("The GCS motor score 'Localizes pain' (Score 5) indicates what level of neuroanatomical involvement?","Purposeful, cortical involvement")
B.Eb=new A.o("Which score on the FOUR Score Eye Response subscale indicates a 'locked-in' state?","4 (Eyelids open, tracking or blinking to command)")
B.EL=new A.o("A Glasgow Outcome Scale (GOS) score of 3 indicates what clinical category?","Severe Disability (conscious but dependent)")
