B.FE=new A.o("According to the Brain Trauma Foundation (BTF) 4th Edition, identify the only Level I recommendation.","Steroids are contraindicated for the treatment of traumatic brain injury.")
B.Ea=new A.o("Which landmark clinical trial demonstrated that methylprednisolone increases mortality in patients with TBI?","The CRASH trial.")
B.G9=new A.o("The current Brain Trauma Foundation guideline (4th Ed) defines the threshold for treating intracranial pressure (ICP) at _____.","> 22 mmHg")
B.Ek=new A.o("What clinical criteria, in addition to a normal CT scan, indicate ICP monitoring in severe TBI patients?","At least two of: age > 40, motor posturing, or SBP < 90 mmHg.")
B.DQ=new A.o("Term: External Ventricular Drain (EVD)","Definition: The gold standard for ICP monitoring that also allows for therapeutic CSF drainage.")
B.Hg=new A.o("At what anatomical landmark must an external ventricular drain (EVD) be calibrated?","The foramen of Monro, which corresponds to the tragus of the ear.")
B.EN=new A.o("Which trial found no significant difference in 6-month mortality between ICP monitor-based management and imaging-based management?","The BEST-TRIP trial.")
B.Gx=new A.o("The standard target range for Cerebral Perfusion Pressure (CPP) in TBI patients is _____.","60-70 mmHg")
