B.GS=new A.o("Cerebral ischemia and increased morbidity are likely to occur when the CPP falls below _____.","50 mmHg")
B.H3=new A.o("Why is mannitol specifically contraindicated in hypotensive TBI patients?","It is an osmotic diuretic that causes volume depletion, potentially worsening hypotension.")
B.Gi=new A.o("When administering hypertonic saline (HTS) for ICP management, serum sodium should be monitored to stay below _____.","160 mEq/L")
