B.DX=new A.o("In the SIBICC tiered algorithm, neuromuscular blockade (e.g., cisatracurium) is classified as a _____ intervention.","Tier 2")
B.GL=new A.o("Identify the primary mechanism by which hyperventilation acutely reduces intracranial pressure.","Induced cerebral vasoconstriction due to decreased PaCO2.")
B.E8=new A.o("Hyperventilation should be avoided during the first 24 hours after injury because _____ is already naturally reduced.","Cerebral blood flow (CBF)")
