B.H4=new A.o("Based on the POLAR and Eurotherm3235 trials, what is the current standard for temperature management in acute TBI?","Controlled normothermia (36.0-37.5 degrees C).")
B.H1=new A.o("According to the CRASH-3 trial, Tranexamic Acid (TXA) significantly reduces head injury death in which specific TBI severity group?","Mild-to-moderate TBI (GCS 9-15).")
