B.EQ=new A.o("Why does the brain have a unique susceptibility to consumptive coagulopathy after injury?","The brain contains the highest concentration of tissue factor of any organ.")
B.H2=new A.o("Term: GFAP (Glial Fibrillary Acidic Protein)","Definition: An FDA-cleared blood biomarker for astrocyte injury used to triage mild TBI.")
B.GU=new A.o("Term: UCH-L1 (Ubiquitin C-terminal Hydrolase L1)","Definition: An FDA-cleared blood biomarker indicating neuronal degradation.")
B.E2=new A.o("What was the primary conclusion of the DECRA trial regarding early bifrontal decompressive craniectomy for diffuse injury?","It decreased ICP but was associated with worse functional outcomes (GOS-E).")
B.GK=new A.o("How did the RESCUEicp trial differ from the DECRA trial regarding the timing of decompressive craniectomy?","RESCUEicp studied craniectomy as a last-resort rescue therapy for refractory ICP.")
