B.GP=new A.o("Identify the three components of the Cushing Triad.","Hypertension, bradycardia, and irregular respirations.")
B.He=new A.o("By which post-injury day does the BTF recommend reaching full nutritional replacement to decrease mortality?","Day 5 to 7.")
B.Hv=new A.o("What is the recommended daily protein intake for a patient with severe TBI?","1.5-2 g/kg/day")
B.Em=new A.o("When should pharmacologic DVT prophylaxis be initiated in a TBI patient if the follow-up CT is stable?","Within 24-48 hours of admission.")
