B.FI=new A.o("Which two medications have the strongest evidence for managing the autonomic surges of Paroxysmal Sympathetic Hyperactivity (PSH)?","Morphine and Propranolol.")
B.F4=new A.o("What is the most common type of hydrocephalus following traumatic brain injury?","Communicating hydrocephalus.")
