B.Fq=new A.o("Subdural hematomas (SDH) are typically caused by the disruption of _____.","Bridging veins.")
B.GA=new A.o("What is the mortality risk associated with a single episode of hypotension (SBP < 90 mmHg) in severe TBI?","It doubles the mortality rate.")
B.G8=new A.o("In the SIBICC algorithm, 'controlled normothermia' targets a temperature of _____.","36.0-37.5 degrees C")
B.Hc=new A.o("Cerebral blood flow is most significantly compromised in which herniation syndrome that results in respiratory arrest?","Tonsillar (Cerebellar) herniation.")
B.Fm=new A.o("Which herniation syndrome involves the cingulate gyrus moving under the falx cerebri, potentially causing contralateral leg weakness?","Subfalcine (Cingulate) herniation.")
B.F0=new A.o("According to the BTF nutrition guidelines, transgastric jejunal feeding is recommended to reduce the risk of _____.","Ventilator-associated pneumonia (VAP).")
