B.Ei=new A.o("In acute TBI, what is the target fibrinogen level to manage brain-specific coagulopathy?","> 1.5-2.0 g/L")
B.Fn=new A.o("Which intracranial monitor cannot be recalibrated after insertion and is prone to measurement drift?","Intraparenchymal monitors (e.g., Codman, Camino).")
B.G4=new A.o("Identify the risk factor associated with the highest incidence (33-50%) of post-traumatic seizures.","Penetrating brain injury.")
B.HE=new A.o("A target PaCO2 of 30-35 mmHg is recommended only as _____ therapy during acute herniation.","Bridge")
B.Fk=new A.o("What is the peak timeframe for the hypermetabolic response following a severe TBI?","2 weeks post-injury.")
B.Hx=new A.o("According to the CRASH-3 trial, what was the effect of TXA on patients with severe TBI (GCS 3-8)?","There was no significant benefit.")
B.F1=new A.o("Which diagnostic test is more sensitive than conventional PT/PTT for detecting the 'brain-specific' coagulopathy of TBI?","Viscoelastic testing (TEG or ROTEM).")
B.Ec=new A.o("Define the 'syndrome of the trephined'.","Neurological deterioration following a craniectomy that often improves after cranioplasty skull replacement.")
B.Fl=new A.o("Which surgical emergency is characterized by a 'lucid interval' followed by rapid deterioration?","Epidural Hematoma (EDH).")
B.Fu=new A.o("For ICP management, the SIBICC algorithm recommends MAP challenges in which tier?","Tier 2")
B.Fe=new A.o("Jugular bulb oxygen saturation (SjvO2) values below _____ suggest cerebral ischemia.","50%")
